summary: Basically adds a small house in Dawnstar
descriptionHtml:
Basically adds a house in dawnstar.

The house is located at the edge of the town, and also features a grindstone and an armor workbench (which didnt exist in the town blacksmith neither).

This is the first mod I ever make, feel free to make suggestions and report bugs.

Feel free to Endorse if you like the house :)

Changelog:
Version 1.2:
-Fixed (probably) a bug reported in which some users would get stucked upon exiting the house
Version 1.1:
-Removed the ugly snow maces on the right of the house
author: Ima1992
